query: SELECT u.user_id, u.name, o.order_id FROM users u LEFT JOIN orders o ON u.user_id = o.user_id
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM products WHERE price > 100
SELECT p.product_id, p.name, c.category_name FROM products p INNER JOIN categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
SELECT AVG(total) FROM orders WHERE status = 'completed'
description: Average order total for completed orders

query: SELECT u.name, COUNT(o.order_id) as order_count FROM users u LEFT JOIN orders o ON u.user_id = o.user_id GROUP BY u.name
SELECT * FROM events WHERE event_type = 'page_view' AND created_at > CURRENT_DATE() - 7
SELECT o.order_id, oi.product_id, p.name FROM orders o INNER JOIN order_items oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id INNER JOIN products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
description: Get order items with product names

query: SELECT DISTINCT country FROM users ORDER BY country
SELECT user_id, email FROM users WHERE email LIKE '%@gmail.com'
SELECT product_id, name, price FROM products WHERE price BETWEEN 50 AND 200 ORDER BY price DESC
SELECT DATE(created_at) as date, COUNT(*) as order_count FROM orders GROUP BY DATE(created_at) ORDER BY date DESC
SELECT u.name, SUM(o.total) as total_spent FROM users u INNER JOIN orders o ON u.user_id = o.user_id GROUP BY u.name HAVING SUM(o.total) > 1000
SELECT p.category_id, COUNT(*) as product_count, AVG(p.price) as avg_price FROM products p GROUP BY p.category_id
